fields.name: Tropical Green Smoothie
fields.ingredients: ["1 cup spinach", "1 cup pineapple chunks", "1 banana", "1 cup almond milk", "1 tbsp honey"]
fields.instructions: Add all ingredients to a blender and blend on high speed until smooth and creamy. If the smoothie is too thick, add a splash of almond milk or water to achieve desired consistency.

fields.name: Peanut Butter Banana Shake
fields.ingredients: ["1 banana", "2 tbsp peanut butter", "1 cup milk", "1 scoop vanilla protein powder", "1 tsp cinnamon"]
fields.instructions: Combine all ingredients in a blender and blend until smooth and creamy. For a thicker shake, add a few ice cubes and blend again briefly.

fields.name: Strawberry Keto Smoothie
fields.ingredients: ["1 cup strawberries", "1 cup unsweetened almond milk", "1/4 cup chia seeds", "1 tbsp MCT oil", "1 scoop vanilla protein powder"]
fields.instructions: In a blender, combine the strawberries, almond milk, chia seeds, MCT oil, and protein powder. Blend on high speed until smooth and creamy, scraping down the sides as needed.

fields.name: Chocolate Avocado Shake
fields.ingredients: ["1 ripe avocado", "1 cup unsweetened almond milk", "2 tbsp cocoa powder", "2 tbsp maple syrup", "1 tsp vanilla extract"]
fields.instructions: Add all ingredients to a high-powered blender and blend until completely smooth and creamy, about 1-2 minutes. If the shake is too thick, add a splash of almond milk to reach desired consistency.

fields.name: Mango Pineapple Vitamin Boost
fields.instructions: Blend all ingredients until smooth. Serve with a slice of pineapple.

fields.name: Keto Coffee Shake
fields.instructions: Blend all ingredients until smooth. Serve with a sprinkle of cocoa powder.

fields.name: Strawberry Cheesecake Milkshake
fields.instructions: Blend all ingredients until smooth. Top with whipped cream and graham cracker crumbs.

fields.name: Gluten-Free Banana Oat Shake
fields.instructions: Combine all ingredients in a blender and blend until smooth. Serve chilled.

fields.name: Vegan Berry Bliss Smoothie
fields.instructions: Blend all ingredients until smooth. Serve immediately.

fields.name: Blueberry Almond Keto Shake
fields.instructions: Blend all ingredients until smooth. Serve with a handful of whole almonds.

fields.name: Tropical Fruit Smoothie
fields.instructions: Blend all ingredients until smooth. Garnish with a pineapple slice.
